{"tid":906532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好羨慕啲識畫畫嘅人?","createTime":"2018-11-18T05:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T12:41:42.000Z","uid":219529,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"090bb478413202ce7b37148b9ed566fbc3d562d8","tid":906532,"uid":219529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"琴日出咗部新iPad咁我見佢support Apple Pencil 但成七百幾蚊諗左陣買唔買好!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰陣時我諗住買支筆返嚟試下畫畫都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以最後都係買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴晚到今朝試咗成日畫出嚟嘅都係小學雞草圖，用小畫家畫都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻覺得藝術係唔可以勉強同埋好羨慕啲識畫畫嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人自學畫畫成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40eebd64257c330620c3b35a9a0885c0c470c2a6","tid":906532,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:33:17.000Z","msg":"你放左幾多時間去學同練先？"},{"pid":"6659d136d6089b9db2a2fb5027c3d34853998c54","tid":906532,"uid":144596,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:34:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2694a5e9b9ed118ba481042f879d13e8242c75ec","tid":906532,"uid":25367,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"琴晚到今朝試咗成日畫出嚟嘅都係小學雞草圖，<span style=\"color: red;\">用小畫家畫都差唔多</span><br />\n<br />\n你諗住買裝備送技術？"},{"pid":"796db6be86d08a7090443049841bc713f7b97178","tid":906532,"uid":219529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2694a5e9b9ed118ba481042f879d13e8242c75ec","tid":906532,"uid":25367,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"琴晚到今朝試咗成日畫出嚟嘅都係小學雞草圖，<span style=\"color: red;\">用小畫家畫都差唔多</span><br />\n<br />\n你諗住買裝備送技術？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:39:38.000Z","msg":"用Mouse畫始終無咁方便,以為有知筆會即時升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然結論就係唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c896ba9037b819f3afd15f710f582841e7c20218","tid":906532,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n買左部cintiq放係度煲醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b9a5b67fc47247982153e515cef58fb491ac14","tid":906532,"uid":219529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:47:07.000Z","msg":"上網見人畫幾筆就掃描到輪廓出黎,自己落手畫連畫個面型都唔識畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61105b309c651595954ce35e73d8d7ebd75c617e","tid":906532,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:51:17.000Z","msg":"我明白, 不過我連裝備都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f148995a04f0c8d02d81171dbb3d44cd37feab9","tid":906532,"uid":136987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:54:45.000Z","msg":"買本教畫畫既書<br />\n學下光影線條點畫<br />\n應該會進步"},{"pid":"a57372c504cc272c9635229a58a8297dbe0bf466","tid":906532,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c896ba9037b819f3afd15f710f582841e7c20218","tid":906532,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n買左部cintiq放係度煲醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:05:32.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n買左部WACOM 24HD 放左係度成一年半 <br />\n實際用既時長唔夠10個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab2b254bf9c0d0948d3d92682ca7a9702a90855","tid":906532,"uid":109432,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:11:46.000Z","msg":"畫畫係要大量練習<br />\n你覺得簡單嘅技巧<br />\n可能人地keep住做幾年先睇落簡單"},{"pid":"